# Personal task files — local to each machine, never shared. Only the
# example template is tracked; every other task file, including any new
# one, stays local. Note that tasks/inbox-brief.md and
# tasks/proactive-calendar.md are runtime dependencies (read by the
# launchd jobs and proactive/sweep.ts) — they must exist locally on any
# machine running those jobs, but they are no longer distributed here.
tasks/*.md
!tasks/EXAMPLE-task.md
